OL,3,C'Life changing' menopause service at
OL,4,CGP practice in Bury
OL,6,FA dedicated menopause service at a GP
OL,7,Fpractice in Bury has been described as
OL,8,F'life changing' by a number of the
OL,9,Fwomen attending it.
OL,11,FNurse consultant, Karen Swift, plus
OL,12,Fcare co-ordinator, Jayne Chapman,
OL,13,Festablished Ribblesdale Medical
OL,14,FPractice's pioneering menopause
OL,15,Fservice in 2023.
OL,17,FIt came about after the women that
OL,18,Fworked at the practice noticed a need
OL,19,Ffor more tailored support for
OL,20,Fmenopausal women.
