OL,3,C'Life changing' menopause service at
OL,4,CGP practice in Bury
OL,6,FJayne Chapman, the GP practice's
OL,7,Fmenopause champion says that her
OL,8,F'menopause nightmare' began in her 30s
OL,9,Fwith heart palpitations and a trip to
OL,10,FA&E.
OL,12,F"At that time no-one immediately
OL,13,Fsuggested HRT and specific advice and
OL,14,Fsupport wasn't readily available." She
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"Inspired by personal experience and
OL,18,Fwith menopausal co-workers, we
OL,19,Frealised there was a desperate
OL,20,Fopportunity to provide help.
