OL,3,C'Life changing' menopause service at
OL,4,CGP practice in Bury
OL,6,F"We wanted to create a one-stop-shop
OL,7,Ffor advice, care and information which
OL,8,Fenabled patients to have the time to
OL,9,Ftalk but also eased the demand on GP
OL,10,Ftime."
OL,12,FThe service includes a structured
OL,13,Fpatient pathway, symptom
OL,14,Fquestionnaires aligned with NICE
OL,15,Fguidance, one-to-one personalised
OL,16,Fsupport and education from the
OL,17,Fmenopause champion, clinical oversight
OL,18,Ffrom a specialist nurse consultant,
OL,19,Fthree-month reviews of HRT patients,
OL,20,Fplus a new, regular Q&A forum and
OL,21,Fsupport group.
