OL,3,C'Life changing' menopause service at
OL,4,CGP practice in Bury
OL,6,FIt has recently been announced by the
OL,7,Fgovernment that menopause questions
OL,8,Fwill be included in NHS health checks
OL,9,Ffor the first time - a move expected
OL,10,Fto benefit almost five million women.
OL,12,FA nurse for almost two decades, Karen
OL,13,FSwift said: "More help is needed for
OL,14,Fall menopausal women. I've been
OL,15,Fperimenopausal since my 30s. I didn't
OL,16,Finitially consider the menopause as a
OL,17,Freason for symptoms when I was young.
OL,26,@uD@MOU
