OL,3,C'Life changing' menopause service at
OL,4,CGP practice in Bury
OL,6,F"I didn't realise a 'hot flush' could
OL,7,Fbe such a soaking wet sweat, and I
OL,8,Fthought I was tired due to a busy
OL,9,Flife. I just tried to cope alone."
OL,11,FAmy Melbourne has been supported by
OL,12,Fthe dedicated service: "It is such a
OL,13,Frelief to be listened to and have your
OL,14,Ffeelings acknowledged.
