OL,3,C'Life changing' menopause service at
OL,4,CGP practice in Bury
OL,6,F"Menopause symptoms made me a
OL,7,Fdifferent person. I had brain fog, I
OL,8,Fwas increasingly emotional over minor
OL,9,Fthings, my mood was really low, I was
OL,10,Fanxious about trivia, I had panic
OL,11,Fattacks, and I couldn't sleep." she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"I mentioned my worries at a routine
OL,15,Fsmear test and was referred to Jayne
OL,16,FChapman, the menopause champion. After
OL,17,Fa long chat - and the opportunity to
OL,18,Fask a million questions - I completed
OL,19,Fa questionnaire and have started HRT. "
