OL,3,C'Life changing' menopause service at
OL,4,CGP practice in Bury
OL,6,F"I can't thank Jayne enough for really
OL,7,Flistening to me, it has been life-
OL,8,Fchanging. Women do need accessible
OL,9,Fhelp, advice and support. If only
OL,10,Fevery woman could access a GP practice
OL,11,Fmenopause champion!"
OL,13,FThe practice continues to refine the
OL,14,Fservice and share learning to help
OL,15,Fother practices enhance menopause care
OL,16,Facross Greater Manchester and beyond.
